The paper deals with the problem of link prediction on encrypted graphs, which involves both cryptography and graph theory. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves algorithms and data structures for graph analysis, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.DB (Databases). Additionally, the paper involves machine learning techniques for link prediction, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
